description: Ella Nova doesn't have much singles match experience but she was a star in season 11 tag team matches. Vivi Marie has never wrestled before, This match was shot prior to the recent tag update in which she was Penny Barber's Partner. Vivi puts up a good effort and is able to gas out Ella Nova in round 2 and 3......is it enough to make a come back and win?
title: Beautiful Blond Ella Nova takes one Saucey Brunette Vivi Marie
